node.text:
Blade off test! Even if any part breaks inside the engine, it should not come out,If a piece that rotates at very high speed breaks off and pierces the body of the engine and comes out of the engine, it may cause the plane to crash.The broken piece may puncture the fuselage of the aircraft and injure the passengers, or crash if the plane is seriously damaged That's why one of the certification tests of the engines is the blade off test. turbine blade is broken off and it is observed whether it will pierce the body of the engine.
